data.title: BIRTHPLACE OF HERBERT HOOVER
data.meta_description: President Herbert Hoover was born on August 10, 1874 in West Branch, Iowa. He was the first President Born west of the Mississippi River. He was born in this small cottage that is part of the Herbert Hoover Nat'l Historical Site in West Branch, Iowa
